2351
01:04:20,560 --> 01:04:22,960
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He returns with his prize in hand.)</font>

2352
01:04:22,830 --> 01:04:23,970
<font size="64">- Hey. - What's that?</font>

2353
01:04:23,970 --> 01:04:24,970
<font size="64">What's that?</font>

2354
01:04:25,330 --> 01:04:29,500
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He returns bashfully with the Gen Z prize.)</font>

2355
01:04:31,040 --> 01:04:32,270
<font size="64">- Hey. - It's a wax-cracking squishy.</font>

2356
01:04:32,570 --> 01:04:34,310
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Nice)</font>

2357
01:04:32,970 --> 01:04:34,380
<font size="64">You got that?</font>

2358
01:04:34,380 --> 01:04:36,680
<font size="64">- You should've chosen time! - You should've picked time!</font>

2359
01:04:36,680 --> 01:04:38,980
<font size="64">Jae Seok, you should've picked time.</font>

2360
01:04:39,110 --> 01:04:41,120
<font size="64">I hoped to get something nice.</font>

2361
01:04:41,120 --> 01:04:44,620
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He exchanged a wax-cracking squishy for an earlier start time.)</font>

2362
01:04:41,420 --> 01:04:43,380
<font size="64">You thought you'd get a tablet or something.</font>

2363
01:04:43,380 --> 01:04:45,820
<font size="64">Yes. Now we should choose time.</font>

2364
01:04:44,650 --> 01:04:48,290
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Current starting time: 4:30am)</font>

2365
01:04:45,820 --> 01:04:48,120
<font size="64">- I wasted an opportunity. - Why not choose time?</font>

2366
01:04:48,120 --> 01:04:49,590
<font size="64">I'll head over, then!</font>

2367
01:04:48,290 --> 01:04:50,660
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Jong Kook, who has 2 coins, sets off.)</font>

2368
01:04:49,720 --> 01:04:50,760
<font size="64">- Good luck! - Go on.</font>

2369
01:04:50,760 --> 01:04:53,360
<font size="64">- Strike! - Time! Turn back time!</font>

2370
01:04:53,360 --> 01:04:56,460
<font size="64">Do we get another chance to use the machine?</font>

2371
01:04:56,460 --> 01:04:58,570
<font size="64">- Once. Our last chance. - Once more.</font>

2372
01:04:58,570 --> 01:05:00,300
<font size="64">How come I never get to go once?</font>

2373
01:05:00,840 --> 01:05:02,770
<font size="64">Who else hasn't seen the machine?</font>

2374
01:05:02,770 --> 01:05:04,370
<font size="64">- Go where? - What do you mean?</font>

2375
01:05:02,870 --> 01:05:04,740
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Seok Jin and Haha...)</font>

2376
01:05:04,370 --> 01:05:05,670
<font size="64">- Me. - You and I.</font>

2377
01:05:04,740 --> 01:05:07,010
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(didn't even get to see the vending machines.)</font>

2378
01:05:05,870 --> 01:05:06,870
<font size="64">Is this our last chance?</font>

2379
01:05:06,870 --> 01:05:08,580
<font size="64">Are you planning to go?</font>

2380
01:05:08,580 --> 01:05:10,980
<font size="64">Of course. I never got to go once.</font>

2381
01:05:10,980 --> 01:05:12,050
<font size="64">Even Ye Eun went.</font>

2382
01:05:12,050 --> 01:05:14,550
<font size="64">You never give up on the hope of winning something.</font>

2383
01:05:12,550 --> 01:05:18,990
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The greedy Seok Sam wants a prize until the end.)</font>

2384
01:05:14,550 --> 01:05:16,620
<font size="64">Never. I always hope.</font>

2385
01:05:16,650 --> 01:05:18,690
<font size="64">I don't give up until the end.</font>

2386
01:05:19,290 --> 01:05:22,820
<font size="64">Okay. 1.87g of gold, premium whiskey,</font>

2387
01:05:19,490 --> 01:05:25,030
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Jong Kook is also scanning the prize list.)</font>

2388
01:05:22,820 --> 01:05:25,160
<font size="64">assorted Korean pork... There are lots of nice stuff.</font>

2389
01:05:25,030 --> 01:05:26,930
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Luxury body wash and cream, sold out)</font>

2390
01:05:25,160 --> 01:05:26,730
<font size="64">This side is better.</font>

2391
01:05:26,730 --> 01:05:28,260
<font size="64">I can give my father-in-law the whiskey.</font>

2392
01:05:26,930 --> 01:05:28,830
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Wax-cracking squishy, sold out)</font>

2393
01:05:28,260 --> 01:05:30,700
<font size="64">The other ones too... Okay.</font>

2394
01:05:28,830 --> 01:05:30,560
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Prize list)</font>

2395
01:05:32,600 --> 01:05:36,100
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Did he get a good prize as he wanted?)</font>

2396
01:05:43,180 --> 01:05:45,950
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Checking the list again)</font>

2397
01:05:45,850 --> 01:05:48,680
<font size="64">Darn it.</font>

2398
01:05:48,680 --> 01:05:52,190
<font size="64">What the heck is a scalp care device?</font>

2399
01:05:52,790 --> 01:05:56,160
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He gathers himself to use his next coin.)</font>

2400
01:05:56,490 --> 01:05:59,390
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(This time, he chose the time vending machine.)</font>

2401
01:05:59,490 --> 01:06:01,160
<font size="64">What number shall I pick?</font>

2402
01:05:59,560 --> 01:06:01,900
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Careful)</font>

2403
01:06:01,960 --> 01:06:04,370
<font size="64">They think people will choose lucky seven,</font>

2404
01:06:04,370 --> 01:06:06,370
<font size="64">so they never put anything good there.</font>

2405
01:06:06,370 --> 01:06:07,540
<font size="64">Never.</font>

2406
01:06:07,970 --> 01:06:10,070
<font size="64">I have a feeling number nine is good.</font>

2407
01:06:10,300 --> 01:06:11,670
<font size="64">I pick number nine.</font>

2408
01:06:12,240 --> 01:06:16,210
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(After waging psychological warfare with himself, he chooses 9.)</font>

2409
01:06:15,840 --> 01:06:16,880
<font size="64">Nine!</font>

2410
01:06:17,350 --> 01:06:19,410
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(What did he get?)</font>

2411
01:06:25,320 --> 01:06:28,560
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He seems to have gotten a good result.)</font>

2412
01:06:29,520 --> 01:06:30,620
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Thumbs up)</font>

2413
01:06:30,460 --> 01:06:33,260
<font size="64">That's crazy. I was drawn to number nine.</font>

2414
01:06:30,620 --> 01:06:33,390
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(How much time did he delay it?)</font>

2415
01:06:33,260 --> 01:06:34,900
<font size="64">I'll go do my thing.</font>

2416
01:06:33,390 --> 01:06:34,700
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ji Hyo heads to the vending machines.)</font>

2417
01:06:35,200 --> 01:06:37,160
<font size="64">Now that I'm here, this machine...</font>

2418
01:06:37,600 --> 01:06:42,070
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(She stares at the prize vending machine.)</font>

2419
01:06:42,700 --> 01:06:45,910
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ji Hyo chose something.)</font>

2420
01:06:45,970 --> 01:06:47,910
<font size="64">Ji Hyo! Don't waver.</font>

2421
01:06:47,910 --> 01:06:50,610
<font size="64">- Choose time. - Seriously. 4:30am is crazy.</font>

2422
01:06:51,110 --> 01:06:52,410
<font size="64">She's empty-handed.</font>

2423
01:06:53,080 --> 01:06:55,020
<font size="64">- What is it? - She has something.</font>

2424
01:06:55,020 --> 01:06:56,380
<font size="64">- In her hand... - What did you get?</font>

2425
01:06:56,780 --> 01:06:58,590
<font size="64">Her bag is fat.</font>

2426
01:06:57,050 --> 01:07:01,260
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Did Ji Hyo pick time or a prize?)</font>

2427
01:06:58,590 --> 01:06:59,990
<font size="64">- It must be gold. - Ji Hyo!</font>

2428
01:07:01,160 --> 01:07:03,090
<font size="64">You all took your turns with the vending machines.</font>

2429
01:07:03,090 --> 01:07:05,530
<font size="64">- The current starting time... - Yes.</font>

2430
01:07:03,320 --> 01:07:06,930
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The current starting time is 4:30am.)</font>

2431
01:07:05,530 --> 01:07:06,660
<font size="64">It was 4:30am.</font>

2432
01:07:06,660 --> 01:07:08,860
<font size="64">- The new time is... - What is it?</font>

2433
01:07:09,360 --> 01:07:11,300
<font size="64">- Is it 6am? - You added ten hours,</font>

2434
01:07:11,300 --> 01:07:13,470
<font size="64">so now it's 14:30, which is 2:30pm.</font>

2435
01:07:11,530 --> 01:07:15,940
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(It changes to 2pm.)</font>

2436
01:07:13,470 --> 01:07:15,140
<font size="64">- This is bad too. - I don't like this.</font>

2437
01:07:15,140 --> 01:07:16,240
<font size="64">What? At 2:30pm?</font>

2438
01:07:20,710 --> 01:07:22,910
<font size="64">- It's 2:30pm. - This is bad too.</font>

2439
01:07:21,180 --> 01:07:24,650
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The starting time went from dawn to early afternoon.)</font>

2440
01:07:22,910 --> 01:07:24,480
<font size="64">- I don't like this. - What? 2:30pm?</font>

2441
01:07:24,480 --> 01:07:26,510
<font size="64">- What the heck is 2pm? - At 2pm...</font>

2442
01:07:26,580 --> 01:07:27,850
<font size="64">No, 2pm is...</font>

2443
01:07:27,850 --> 01:07:30,520
<font size="64">- That's the worst. - We can't do 2pm.</font>

2444
01:07:30,680 --> 01:07:33,390
<font size="64">Two in the afternoon is just as awkward.</font>

2445
01:07:33,390 --> 01:07:35,090
<font size="64">She added extra hours too!</font>

2446
01:07:35,120 --> 01:07:36,860
<font size="64">- I got plus... - I got plus seven,</font>

2447
01:07:35,790 --> 01:07:38,630
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Did Ji Hyo as well as Jong Kook pick time?)</font>

2448
01:07:36,860 --> 01:07:39,090
<font size="64">so I thought 10:30am was great.</font>

2449
01:07:44,530 --> 01:07:46,970
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Current starting time: 11:30am)</font>

2450
01:07:46,900 --> 01:07:49,570
<font size="64">That's crazy. I was drawn to number nine.</font>

2451
01:07:46,970 --> 01:07:49,640
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He was pleased with the ideal result.)</font>

2452
01:07:49,970 --> 01:07:51,240
<font size="64">I'll go with time.</font>

2453
01:07:55,540 --> 01:07:58,610
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ji Hyo got plus 3 hours.)</font>

2454
01:07:58,510 --> 01:08:02,320
<font size="64">I got plus seven, so I thought 10:30am was great.</font>

2455
01:07:59,080 --> 01:08:02,380
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Ji Hyo's 3 hours and Jong Kook's 7 delays starting time by 10 hours.)</font>

2456
01:08:02,450 --> 01:08:05,320
<font size="64">- What do we do in the morning? - Nothing.</font>

2457
01:08:02,680 --> 01:08:05,320
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The morning person doesn't like it.)</font>

2458
01:08:05,320 --> 01:08:12,360
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Current starting time: 2:30pm)</font>

2459
01:08:05,320 --> 01:08:08,360
<font size="64">I don't like 2pm. It's a weird time.</font>

2460
01:08:08,360 --> 01:08:09,760
<font size="64">We must go back.</font>

2461
01:08:09,760 --> 01:08:10,830
<font size="64">- Yes. - We need...</font>

2462
01:08:10,830 --> 01:08:12,290
<font size="64">- a negative number. - Minus something.</font>

2463
01:08:12,290 --> 01:08:14,760
<font size="64">- We need minus five or below. - Gosh...</font>

2464
01:08:14,760 --> 01:08:16,300
<font size="64">- Let's go back. - We need a minus number.</font>

2465
01:08:16,300 --> 01:08:17,830
<font size="64">What, 2:30pm?</font>

2466
01:08:17,830 --> 01:08:20,170
<font size="64">The previous time is better than this.</font>

2467
01:08:18,270 --> 01:08:23,700
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Now, their goal is to move the starting time back.)</font>

2468
01:08:20,170 --> 01:08:21,970
<font size="64">- Early is better. - We get up early anyway.</font>

2469
01:08:21,970 --> 01:08:24,240
<font size="64">I prefer to get up at midnight or 1am.</font>

2470
01:08:24,370 --> 01:08:26,910
<font size="64">You can change the time through this last mission.</font>

2471
01:08:24,510 --> 01:08:28,140
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They only have one chance to change the time.)</font>

2472
01:08:26,910 --> 01:08:28,180
<font size="64">- Okay, let's go. - Let's do it.</font>

2473
01:08:28,180 --> 01:08:29,480
<font size="64">We must do something.</font>

2474
01:08:29,210 --> 01:08:34,920
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Will they be able to go to work at their preferred time?)</font>

2475
01:08:29,480 --> 01:08:31,580
<font size="64">- An afternoon... - Let's go.</font>

2476
01:08:31,650 --> 01:08:33,280
<font size="64">Starting at 2:30pm is...</font>

2477
01:08:33,280 --> 01:08:35,850
<font size="64">Could we end up starting in the evening?</font>

2478
01:08:35,850 --> 01:08:37,490
<font size="64">What's this? Gosh.</font>

2479
01:08:36,850 --> 01:08:40,550
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(There are familiar tables and partitions inside.)</font>

2480
01:08:37,490 --> 01:08:38,550
<font size="64">It looks like a quiz.</font>

2481
01:08:38,850 --> 01:08:41,220
<font size="64">Goodness. Is it a quiz?</font>

2482
01:08:41,260 --> 01:08:42,960
<font size="64">- I'll get it right. - It's cool in here.</font>

2483
01:08:41,390 --> 01:08:43,490
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Taking the answer seat)</font>

2484
01:08:42,960 --> 01:08:45,860
<font size="64">- What is this for? - Where should I sit?</font>

2485
01:08:43,920 --> 01:08:46,860
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They take their seats, expecting a quiz.)</font>

2486
01:08:45,930 --> 01:08:47,460
<font size="64">Do we sit just anywhere?</font>

2487
01:08:47,390 --> 01:08:49,460
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Sit next to me.)</font>

2488
01:08:47,460 --> 01:08:48,530
<font size="64">Can I sit where I want?</font>

2489
01:08:49,960 --> 01:08:51,500
<font size="64">- Hey. - What?</font>

2490
01:08:50,130 --> 01:08:51,900
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Spotting)</font>

2491
01:08:51,630 --> 01:08:52,930
<font size="64">Why did you beckon Jong Kook over?</font>

2492
01:08:52,930 --> 01:08:54,200
<font size="64">- When we play a game... - Just in case.</font>

2493
01:08:54,200 --> 01:08:55,840
<font size="64">- Why did you beckon Jong Kook over? - What?</font>

2494
01:08:54,840 --> 01:08:57,740
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Empty Head Ji is already making them nervous.)</font>

2495
01:08:56,300 --> 01:08:57,340
<font size="64">- Seriously. - Let's go.</font>

2496
01:08:57,340 --> 01:08:59,170
<font size="64">Here comes the third mission...</font>

2497
01:08:59,170 --> 01:09:00,610
<font size="64">- to win additional coins. - Okay.</font>

2498
01:09:00,610 --> 01:09:01,940
<font size="64">You'll play the Different Dreams Quiz...</font>

2499
01:09:01,940 --> 01:09:03,340
<font size="64">- as a team. - What is it?</font>

2500
01:09:03,340 --> 01:09:04,850
<font size="64">- The answers will be different. - Different Dreams Quiz.</font>

2501
01:09:04,850 --> 01:09:07,820
<font size="64">All the members except for the guesser...</font>

2502
01:09:07,720 --> 01:09:13,320
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Answer: Running Man)</font>

2503
01:09:07,820 --> 01:09:09,750
<font size="64">will see the answer the production crew has provided...</font>

2504
01:09:09,780 --> 01:09:13,420
<font size="64">and write down a related keyword that'll help with guessing.</font>

2505
01:09:13,320 --> 01:09:19,160
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Yu Jae Seok, SBS, variety show, running, Sunday, long-standing)</font>

2506
01:09:13,720 --> 01:09:15,660
<font size="64">But they can't write down a keyword that contains...</font>

2507
01:09:15,660 --> 01:09:17,860
<font size="64">the category of the answer...</font>

2508
01:09:17,860 --> 01:09:19,190
<font size="64">- or syllables from the answer. - Of course not.</font>

2509
01:09:19,290 --> 01:09:21,200
<font size="64">Before the guesser sees the keywords,</font>

2510
01:09:21,200 --> 01:09:22,860
<font size="64">you'll reveal the keywords...</font>

2511
01:09:22,860 --> 01:09:24,970
<font size="64">and delete the overlapping ones.</font>

2512
01:09:26,670 --> 01:09:29,540
<font size="64">- If the answer is Running Man... - Okay.</font>

2513
01:09:27,970 --> 01:09:29,800
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Keyword: Running Man)</font>

2514
01:09:29,540 --> 01:09:31,870
<font size="64">and three people write down "Yu Jae Seok,"</font>

2515
01:09:29,800 --> 01:09:32,870
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Yu Jae Seok, SBS, Yu Jae Seok, Yu Jae Seok, Sunday, long-standing)</font>

2516
01:09:31,870 --> 01:09:34,410
<font size="64">- the guesser won't see it. - That makes sense.</font>

2517
01:09:32,870 --> 01:09:34,680
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The guesser can't see the overlapping keywords.)</font>

2518
01:09:34,580 --> 01:09:38,410
<font size="64">The guesser will guess the answer from the remaining keywords.</font>

2519
01:09:35,080 --> 01:09:39,010
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The key is to predict keywords that no one else will choose.)</font>

2520
01:09:38,410 --> 01:09:40,010
<font size="64">There will be seven questions in total.</font>

2521
01:09:40,010 --> 01:09:41,350
<font size="64">You'll get a number of coins that correspond with...</font>

2522
01:09:41,350 --> 01:09:42,880
<font size="64">the number of correct answers.</font>

2523
01:09:42,880 --> 01:09:44,120
<font size="64">This is an opportunity.</font>

2524
01:09:44,120 --> 01:09:45,220
<font size="64">That means...</font>

2525
01:09:44,650 --> 01:09:45,890
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Current starting time: 2:30pm)</font>

2526
01:09:45,220 --> 01:09:46,920
<font size="64">- we need to do well. - This is our chance.</font>

2527
01:09:45,890 --> 01:09:50,090
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(It's a great chance to move up the starting time.)</font>

2528
01:09:46,990 --> 01:09:48,490
<font size="64">This is an opportunity.</font>

2529
01:09:48,490 --> 01:09:49,860
<font size="64">Let's do this.</font>

2530
01:09:50,190 --> 01:09:51,560
<font size="64">Let's switch places.</font>

2531
01:09:51,560 --> 01:09:52,630
<font size="64">- Four-character idioms work. - Listen.</font>

2532
01:09:52,630 --> 01:09:54,860
<font size="64">- Four-character idioms work, right? - The guesser is important.</font>

2533
01:09:52,990 --> 01:09:56,100
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Empty Head Captain immediately backs off.)</font>

2534
01:09:54,860 --> 01:09:56,030
<font size="64">- Let's switch places. - You need to guess correctly.</font>

2535
01:09:56,030 --> 01:09:57,100
<font size="64">Let's switch places. I'll guess the answers.</font>

2536
01:09:57,100 --> 01:09:58,570
<font size="64">- Okay. Go ahead. - Okay.</font>

2537
01:09:58,630 --> 01:10:00,670
<font size="64">- Guess from our keywords. - Yes.</font>

2538
01:09:58,870 --> 01:10:02,400
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Kim Muscles, who has a sharp mind, will try to guess.)</font>

2539
01:10:01,200 --> 01:10:02,370
<font size="64">Jong Kook is a choice.</font>

2540
01:10:02,840 --> 01:10:04,970
<font size="64">If you don't understand the answer,</font>

2541
01:10:05,440 --> 01:10:07,370
<font size="64">- don't make things up. - Seriously.</font>

2542
01:10:07,910 --> 01:10:09,740
